title: Ocean

Don't worry, momma

I swear I won't complain no more

Doesn't matter if we're rich or poor

Found out that we don't live to die

Even though there is no reason why



Don't worry, momma

'Cause I'm not afraid, I'm not afraid

Don't worry, momma

'Cause I'm on my way

I'm on my way to the ocean

Oh, oh, oh

Oh oh oh, oh oh oh

Oh, oh, oh

Oh oh oh, oh oh oh

To the ocean



To the ocean, to the ocean, to the ocean

To the ocean

Oh, oh, oh

Oh oh oh, oh oh oh

Oh, oh, oh

Oh oh oh, oh oh oh



To the ocean
